Package bd.gene_network.logic

Class Summary
BinaryTimingDiagramObserver This class produces the desired input signal over time.
LogicGeneNetworkSettings This class holds the global parameters for the Device optimization problem.
LogicGeneNetworkSimulation Class used to run stochastic simulations on a gene network.
SimAllLogicGeneNetworks Run a simulation on all possible gene networks for a given template with the available bioparts database.
SimLogicGeneNetwork Run a simulation on a given gene network.
SimRandomLogicGeneNetwork Run a simulation on a randomly selected device from all possible devices for a given template and bioparts database.
